{"data": [{"id": "4741764", "title": "Realty Income: What Could Turn The Tide?", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161936018/image_2161936018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"global warming ocean level rise on waterfront in europe\" data-id=\"2161936018\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161936018/image_2161936018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161936018/image_2161936018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161936018/image_2161936018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161936018/image_2161936018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161936018/image_2161936018.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161936018/image_2161936018.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161936018/image_2161936018.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161936018/image_2161936018.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">galitskaya/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p><strong>Steady as she goes</strong>: <em>Used to describe a ship sailing steady. It can be defined as being careful, steady, and being consistent. </em></p> <p>My days of dealing with rough seas or changing tides while docked are long gone since my</p>", "image": "http