s a dividend growth investor, my goal is simple: I aim to own businesses that are reliable dividend payers. This is because I plan to ultimately</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355702861/image_1355702861.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742205-coca-cola-stock-dividend-king-approaching-my-buy-zone-now-reiterate-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 15:15:00"}, {"id": "4742301", "title": "Mortgage Rate Headwinds, Hurricanes Take Steam Out Of U.S. New Home Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157590565/image_157590565.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Real Estate\" data-id=\"157590565\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157590565/image_157590565.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157590565/image_157590565.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157590565/image_157590565.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157590565/image_157590565.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157590565/image_157590565.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157590565/image_157590565.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157590565/image_157590565.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157590565/image_157590565.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">alexsl</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>As <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4731100-new-home-sales-rise-mortgage-rates-fall-in-september-2024-headwinds-build-in-october\" rel=\"noopener\">expected</a>, October 2024's rebound in mortgage rates helped take steam out of the U.S. new home market.</p> <p>The 30-year conventional fixed rate mortgage rose from 6.08% at the end of September 2024 to 6.72% at the end of October. The sales</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157590565/image_157590565.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742301-mortgage-rate-headwinds-hurricanes-take-steam-out-of-us-new-home-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 15:10:00"}, {"id": "4742227", "title": "If I Could Only Buy 3 REITs In December 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393356971/image_1393356971.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"REIT. Real estate investment trust. Financial Market. Hand pressing button on screen\" data-id=\"1393356971\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"738px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393356971/image_1393356971.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393356971/image_1393356971.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393356971/image_1393356971.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393356971/image_1393356971.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393356971/image_1393356971.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393356971/image_1393356971.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393356971/image_1393356971.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalph